<h2>Latest News</h2>
<p><br>
<h4>AbeBooks has Heyer on top 10 bestsellers list</h4>
"Georgette Who? Meet the Author Who Outsells Rowling, Dickens and Patterson"<br>
<a href="http://www.abebooks.co.uk/books/historical-regency-romance-bestselling-detective/georgette-heyer.shtml?cm_mmc=nl-_-nl-_-110630-h00-georgetUA-_-01cta">AbeBooks has announced</a> 
that in their 15 year history of their company, Georgette Heyer is in the top 10
bestselling authors!
<p><br>
<h4>eBooks on Amazon UK and US</h4>
<address>
The Kindle-ready eBooks are out on Amazon - both the 
<a href="http://www.amazon.co.uk/s/qid=1298843625/ref=sr_st?keywords=georgette+heyer&page=1&rh=n%3A341677031%2Cn%3A!341678031%2Ck%3Ageorgette+heyer&sort=daterank">UK</a> and 
<a href="http://www.amazon.com/s/qid=1298843538/ref=sr_st?keywords=georgette+heyer&page=1&rh=n%3A133140011%2Cn%3A!133141011%2Ck%3Ageorgette+heyer&sort=daterank">USA</a> sites.  
</address>
<p><br>
<h4>The Reluctant Widow movie</h4>
<address>
The entire movie has been posted to YouTube -- follow <a href="movies.html">my links on the movie page</a> for the 9 sections (ends a little prematurely).
</address>
<p><br>
